text: Darya Muravyeva (born 18 August 1998) is a Kazakhstani female water polo player. She competed for the Kazakhstan women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * water-polo-kazakh-ladies-striving-to- become-best-asian-team * water-polo-reports-women-day-1 Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani water polo players
